<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Job #<%= job.id %> – No Quotes Received</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .box {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 160px;
      height: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer-links {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #007bff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="<%= homeUrl || 'http://localhost:3000' %>">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl || (baseUrl + '/img/logo-true.svg') %>" alt="My Car Quote Logo">
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Hello <%= customerName %>,</h2>

    <p>We’re sorry to inform you that your request (Job <strong>#<%= job.id %></strong>) has been automatically closed after 48 hours because no bodyshops submitted quotes, even after your extension.</p>

    <p>You can <a href="<%= newRequestUrl || (baseUrl + '/jobs/upload') %>">submit a new request</a> at any time or return to our <a href="<%= homeUrl || baseUrl %>">home page</a>.</p>

    <p>Thank you for using My Car Quote.</p>

    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="<%= homeUrl || baseUrl %>">Home</a> |
      <a href="<%= newRequestUrl || (baseUrl + '/jobs/upload') %>">New Request</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
